snippet.textDisplay: Oh my gosh this is horrendous, truly horrendous interviewing. Can someone please explain to me why we are being called “anti-vaxxers”? It makes me so angry and cross and I try not to engage in the “narrative” but the BBC is driving this agenda, is this because it’s “owned” by the Govt! It is us Brits who pay for the TV Licence, not the Govt. body autonomy is what the medical profession tends to go with when it suits them, but not in this instance when the rest of us want to exercise this. Why are we not labelled, “Pro choice”. It just shows the bloody ignorance and I don’t understand why they are still driving this agenda. I saw a BBC interview yesterday and it was asking so called “anti vaxxers” why they are being so selfish! The girl who was interviewed clearly had her head on her shoulders so to speak and yet she was belittled for her views. The flipping C is nearly over and yet why are they still “shaming” people publicly about their choices! Thank you for this video and I feel sad that he was put in this awful position but it is time we all speak up and I have seen some leading figures starting to feel they been duped over the vaccine and they didn’t get the booster as a result! This is the “woke” culture we need now and we should be claiming compensation for the loss of personal freedoms and rights. The world is changing, people are speaking up and this old patriarchy and bullying has no space here now!
